    "The detailed technical aspects will be elaborated in Section 4.2.",
    "Agent Collaboration WorkflowAgents with tailored functions collaboratively work together to edit based on user commands.",
    "The project manager orchestrates and dispatches instructions to editing agents.",
    "The editing agents form two teams: background generation and foreground generation.",
    "For background generation, the background rendering agent generates rendered images using the extrinsic parameters from the view adjustment agent, followed by inpainting by the vehicle deleting agent."
